{
  "stem": "27150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he finished this school, and we helped, you see, that means, and I was a year after, was a very good school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, we were very well drilled in accountancy and merchandising and shopping, and sort of like the high schools or so.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, and that means, the excursions, other than to the theater or exhibition, we spent a couple of days in, in banks, you know, and big factories.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, we were shown machines and et cetera.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we spent the-- in the second and third year, spent a day on the stock exchange.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was a school founded by the Chamber of Commerce, the Warsaw Chamber of Commerce, which was a Polish institution, but big first category businessmen could belong, too.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the school, you see, that means, we started five Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We finished three, because the other went to work or apprenticeship, or--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like 35 or 40, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None, practically none.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, that means we-- as I told you before, my parents were cheated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew Hebrew, but we didn't know the, the prayers, you see, the service routine-- you know, like in the cheders, in the religious school there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we could speak Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you see, on the New Year or atonement days-- you see that was the days that we had to go, you know, because we-- not to hurt the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, we could read, and that's all we read-- this and this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And until now, you see, I can read Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I can, sort of, follow the cantor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly, you see, on holidays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, that means, as a child, you see, that means old people were attending, and we played football in the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
